<paragraph pageId="25" pageNumber="104">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="25" pageNumber="104">Wide-spread throughout the arid and temperate areas of the southern part of mainland Australia and Tasmania (Fig. 7).</paragraph>
